        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(gateway): dedupe probe warnings by gateway identity",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Fixes #69135 by suppressing `multiple_gateways` only when reachable probe targets report the same provable gateway self identity.\n- Gateway self presence now exposes a process-level `instanceId`; same-host/same-config ambiguity without a process/device identity remains conservative and still warns.\n- SSH tunnel, proxy/TLS URL, and configured remote URL can resolve to the same gateway even when transport ports differ.\n- Docs and regression tests now describe distinct, same, and identity-ambiguous gateway cases.\n\n## Verification\n\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/infra/system-presence.test.ts src/infra/system-presence.version.test.ts src/commands/gateway-presence.test.ts src/commands/gateway-status/output.test.ts --reporter=dot` -> 4 files, 22 tests passed\n- `./node_modules/.bin/oxfmt --check --threads=1 src/infra/system-presence.ts docs/cli/gateway.md docs/gateway/index.md docs/gateway/multiple-gateways.md docs/gateway/troubleshooting.md src/commands/gateway-presence.test.ts src/commands/gateway-presence.ts src/commands/gateway-status/output.test.ts src/commands/gateway-status/output.ts`\n- `./node_modules/.bin/oxlint src/infra/system-presence.ts src/commands/gateway-presence.test.ts src/commands/gateway-presence.ts src/commands/gateway-status/output.test.ts src/commands/gateway-status/output.ts`\n- `git diff --check refs/remotes/upstream-safe/main...HEAD`\n- `git diff --check`\n- Earlier on this PR: `codex review --base refs/remotes/upstream-safe/main` -> no discrete regression found\n\nSigned head: `dace167672c67f16580f5cac36f5eee5ee95fbf8`.",
